name: Jira SI Update - Salesforce Case
description:
**Trigger**: trigger when any SI jira is updated.

**Description**: When a Case's SupportInternalStatus is set to "Waiting on Engineering Qualification" and has an SI Jira attached, if the SI Jira changes to any of the following statuses, change the SupportInternalStatus to "With Support"
Missing required information
Waiting for customer
Waiting for support
Closed

**Actions**: It is updating  support internal status field in case object from "Waiting on Engineering Qualification"  to "With Support"
